{"tid":1223122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（好撚重要）提防五毛大軍洗版注意 （2）","createTime":"2019-06-14T15:33:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T16:24:17.000Z","uid":15394,"like":131,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"8ab69bf50d4492dea25ba6870cb1d1a9bc4e31d4","tid":1223122,"uid":15394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T15:33:00.000Z","msg":"（第1個post已經沉撚左，再開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五毛大軍洗版注意</span></span><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">技倆 一 </span>: 起臭雞底 / 有朋友支持警察xxxxxxx<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">技倆 二</span> : 引起罵戰 (耶撚唱歌有乜用)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">技倆 三</span> : 未證實既消息 (8點記者會)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">技倆 四</span> : 花邊新聞 (例如田蕊妮杜汶澤)<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n全部目的就係為左<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">引起討論</span></span><br />\n<br />\n越多人入去留comment，<br />\n個post越易上熱門，<br />\n即係 <span style=\"color: red;\">可以令到其他有用既熱門post拉到落黎</span>！<br />\n<br />\n記住<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要做對大局有幫助既野<br />\n小事就打贏場仗先處理</span></span><br />\n<br />\n五毛有意將 <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">實用</span> 既風氣 <br />\n變返 <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">無意義</span> 既閒談<br />\n<br />\n唔好中伏呀！！！！！"},{"pid":"87f11e2b64ffbda0c54a3150b990647d5d89af11","tid":1223122,"uid":104719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T15:33:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a1c3b01fd655b668016e654d49ed6a7a32b35867","tid":1223122,"uid":15394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":